msgid "# `pgroonga_crash_safer.max_recovery_threads` parameter"
msgstr ""

msgid "Since 3.1.9."
msgstr "3.1.9で追加"

msgid "## Summary"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "`pgroonga_crash_safer.max_recovery_threads` parameter specifies the number of threads for recovery of broken Groonga indexes."
msgstr "`pgroonga_crash_safer.max_recovery_threads` パラメータは壊れたGroongaインデクスの復旧行うスレッド数を指定します。"

msgid ""
"* The default is `0`, which means disabled\n"
"* Use all CPUs in the environment at `-1`\n"
"* Use CPU for that number if `1` or later is set"
msgstr ""
"* デフォルトは `0` でこれは無効を意味します\n"
"* 環境にあるすべてのCPUを使う場合は `-1` を設定します\n"
"* `1` 以上の値を設定すると、設定された数のCPUを使います"

msgid "## Syntax"
msgstr "## 構文"

msgid "In `postgresql.conf`:"
msgstr "`postgresql.conf` の場合"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"pgroonga_crash_safer.max_recovery_threads = number_of_threads\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使い方"

msgid "Here is an example to specify `-1`:"
msgstr "`-1` を指定する例です。"

msgid ""
"```text\n"
"pgroonga_crash_safer.max_recovery_threads = -1\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

